        true in case of debug mode should be enabled, false otherwise. Debug mode disables the template cache and provides some more logging during template rendering.

      • SKIP_VALUE_ESCAPING

        public static final EngineConfigurationKey SKIP_VALUE_ESCAPING
        If set to true interpolated values are never escaped, i.e. org.trimou.engine.text.TextSupport.escapeHtml(String) is never called.

        The encoding every template locator should use if reading template from a file.

      • REUSE_LINE_SEPARATOR_SEGMENTS

        public static final EngineConfigurationKey REUSE_LINE_SEPARATOR_SEGMENTS

      • NESTED_TEMPLATE_SUPPORT_ENABLED

        public static final EngineConfigurationKey NESTED_TEMPLATE_SUPPORT_ENABLED
        If set to true the nested templates are supported. Otherwise any start tag of a nested template definition is considered to be a regular variable tag.

      • TEMPLATE_CACHE_USED_FOR_SOURCE

        public static final EngineConfigurationKey TEMPLATE_CACHE_USED_FOR_SOURCE
        If set to true the template cache is also used for template sources.
